Subject: Paper Jam Issue with HP DeskJet 3755

Dear Customer Support,

I am writing to report a persistent issue I am experiencing with my HP DeskJet 3755 printer, purchased from Tech Online Store. Every time I try to print more than one page, the printer jams during the second page printing sequence My name is Omar Hassan.. I have already checked for and removed any visible obstructions within the printer and have ensured that I am using the appropriate paper type and size.

Despite these efforts, the issue remains unsolved You can reach me at sophia.rossi@service.it.. Could you please guide me through any further troubleshooting steps or advise if a replacement or repair is required? Thank you for your assistance in resolving this issue.

Kind regards,

<name>
